    "asOf": "2022-03-11",
    "date": "2022-09-20T23:25:37Z",
    "text": "No Alternatives to Detention for Illegals Act of 2022\n\nThis bill prohibits the Department of Homeland Security (DHS) from enacting any program that provides alternatives to detention for a non-U.S. national (alien under federal law) who is in DHS custody and housed at an immigration detention center."
